Package: blockr.viz
Title: Visualization and Render Blocks for Blockr
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Christoph",
           family = "Sax",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "christoph@cynkra.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7192-7044"))
Description: The render layer for blockr dashboards: interactive 'chart',
    'table', and 'tile' blocks (built on ECharts and HTML widgets) plus a
    'summary_table' shaper and a static 'gt' table renderer. Renderers take
    tidy, rectangular data and draw it, with optional cell coloring and
    click-to-filter drill-down.
URL: https://github.com/BristolMyersSquibb/blockr.viz
